title: Jimmie Allen On Being A Black Country Artist + Lunchbox Prank Calls Zoos + Guys Get Their Pics Roasted Online
itunes:title: Jimmie Allen On Being A Black Country Artist + Lunchbox Prank Calls Zoos + Guys Get Their Pics Roasted Online
description:
We talk with Jimmie Allen about everything going on in the world right now and what it’s like to be a black artist in country music. Lunchbox calls zoos to let them know the animals are out of their cages...except they are animals that would NEVER be in cages. Plus, the guys posted photos on Reddit to get roasted. They all read back their Top 5 worst comments!
